Selection.name: Selection
Selection.documentation: Represents a set of nodes in a DOM tree. https://grafana.com/docs/k6/latest/javascript-api/k6-html/selection/

attr.name: attr
attr.documentation: Get the value of an attribute for the first element in the Selection. https://grafana.com/docs/k6/latest/javascript-api/k6-html/selection/selection-attr/

children.name: children
children.documentation: Get the children of each element in the set of matched elements, optionally filtered by a selector. https://grafana.com/docs/k6/latest/javascript-api/k6-html/selection/selection-children/

closest.name: closest
closest.documentation: For each element in the set, get the first element that matches the selector by testing the element itself and traversing up through its ancestors in the DOM tree. https://grafana.com/docs/k6/latest/javascript-api/k6-html/selection/selection-closest/

contents.name: contents
contents.documentation: Get the children of each element in the set of matched elements, including text and comment nodes. https://grafana.com/docs/k6/latest/javascript-api/k6-html/selection/selection-contents/

data.name: data
data.documentation: Return the value at the named data store for the first element in the set of matched elements. https://grafana.com/docs/k6/latest/javascript-api/k6-html/selection/selection-data/

params.name: key
params.documentation: - A string naming the piece of data to set.\

returns.documentation: value at the named data store.

each.name: each
each.documentation: Iterate over a Selection (k6/html), executing a function for each matched element. https://grafana.com/docs/k6/latest/javascript-api/k6-html/selection/selection-each/

params.name: handler
params.documentation: - Logic to execute for each element.

eq.name: eq
eq.documentation: Reduce the set of matched elements to the one at the specified index. https://grafana.com/docs/k6/latest/javascript-api/k6-html/selection/selection-eq/

params.name: index
params.documentation: - An integer indicating the 0-based position of the element.

filter.name: filter
filter.documentation: Reduce the set of matched elements to those that match the selector or pass the function's test. https://grafana.com/docs/k6/latest/javascript-api/k6-html/selection/selection-filter/

params.name: selector
params.documentation: - A selection to match elements against.

find.name: find
find.documentation: Find the selection descendants, filtered by a selector. https://grafana.com/docs/k6/latest/javascript-api/k6-html/selection/selection-find/

first.name: first
first.documentation: Reduce the set of matched elements to the first. https://grafana.com/docs/k6/latest/javascript-api/k6-html/selection/selection-first/

get.name: get
get.documentation: Retrieve the element matched by the selector. https://grafana.com/docs/k6/latest/javascript-api/k6-html/selection/selection-get/

params.name: index
params.documentation: - A zero-based integer indicating which element to retrieve.

has.name: has
has.documentation: Reduce the set of matched elements to those that have a descendant that matches the selector. https://grafana.com/docs/k6/latest/javascript-api/k6-html/selection/selection-has/

html.name: html
html.documentation: Get the HTML contents of the first element. https://grafana.com/docs/k6/latest/javascript-api/k6-html/selection/selection-html/

returns.documentation: HTML content of the first element.

is.name: is
is.documentation: Check the current matched set of elements against a selector or element and return true if at least one of these elements matches the given arguments. https://grafana.com/docs/k6/latest/javascript-api/k6-html/selection/selection-is/

returns.documentation: selector matched at least one element.

last.name: last
last.documentation: Reduce the set of matched elements to the final one. https://grafana.com/docs/k6/latest/javascript-api/k6-html/selection/selection-last/

map.name: map
map.documentation: Pass each element in the current matched set through a function, producing a new Array containing the return values. https://grafana.com/docs/k6/latest/javascript-api/k6-html/selection/selection-map/

params.name: mapper
params.documentation: - Procedure to execute on each element.

next.name: next
next.documentation: Get the immediately following sibling of each element. https://grafana.com/docs/k6/latest/javascript-api/k6-html/selection/selection-next/

nextAll.name: nextAll
nextAll.documentation: Get all following siblings of each element, optionally filtered by a selector. https://grafana.com/docs/k6/latest/javascript-api/k6-html/selection/selection-nextall/

nextUntil.name: nextUntil
nextUntil.documentation: Get all following siblings of each element up to but not including the element matched by the selector. https://grafana.com/docs/k6/latest/javascript-api/k6-html/selection/selection-nextuntil/

params.name: selector
params.documentation: - A function used as a test for each element in the set.

parent.name: parent
parent.documentation: Get the parent of each element, optionally filtered by a selector. https://grafana.com/docs/k6/latest/javascript-api/k6-html/selection/selection-parent/

parents.name: parents
parents.documentation: Get the ancestors of each element, optionally filtered by a selector. https://grafana.com/docs/k6/latest/javascript-api/k6-html/selection/selection-parents/

parentsUntil.name: parentsUntil
parentsUntil.documentation: Get the ancestors of each element, up to but not including the element matched by the selector. https://grafana.com/docs/k6/latest/javascript-api/k6-html/selection/selection-parentsuntil/

prev.name: prev
prev.documentation: Get the immediately preceding sibling of each element. https://grafana.com/docs/k6/latest/javascript-api/k6-html/selection/selection-prev/

prevAll.name: prevAll
prevAll.documentation: Get all preceding siblings of each element, optionally filtered by a selector. https://grafana.com/docs/k6/latest/javascript-api/k6-html/selection/selection-prevall/

prevUntil.name: prevUntil
prevUntil.documentation: Get all preceding siblings of each element up to but not including the element matched by the selector. https://grafana.com/docs/k6/latest/javascript-api/k6-html/selection/selection-prevuntil/

serialize.name: serialize
serialize.documentation: Encode a set of form elements as a string in standard URL-encoded notation for submission. https://grafana.com/docs/k6/latest/javascript-api/k6-html/selection/selection-serialize/

returns.documentation: representation of the form or form elements.

serializeArray.name: serializeArray
serializeArray.documentation: Encode a set of form elements as an array of name-value objects. `[{ name: "name", value: "value" }, ... ]` https://grafana.com/docs/k6/latest/javascript-api/k6-html/selection/selection-serializearray/

returns.documentation: of name value objects of the form or form elements.

serializeObject.name: serializeObject
serializeObject.documentation: Encode a set of form elements as an object. `{ inputName: "value", checkboxName: "value", ... }` https://grafana.com/docs/k6/latest/javascript-api/k6-html/selection/selection-serializeobject/

returns.documentation: representation of the form or form elements, key is field name and value is field value.

size.name: size
size.documentation: Return the number of elements in the selection. https://grafana.com/docs/k6/latest/javascript-api/k6-html/selection/selection-size/

returns.documentation: number of elements in the selection.

slice.name: slice
slice.documentation: Reduce the set of elements to a subset specified by a range of indices. https://grafana.com/docs/k6/latest/javascript-api/k6-html/selection/selection-slice/

params.name: start
params.documentation: - An integer indicating the 0-based position at which the elements begin to be selected.

params.name: end
params.documentation: - An integer indicating the 0-based position at which the elements stop being selected.

text.name: text
text.documentation: Get the text content of the selection. https://grafana.com/docs/k6/latest/javascript-api/k6-html/selection/selection-text/

toArray.name: toArray
toArray.documentation: Retrieve all the elements contained in the selection as an array. https://grafana.com/docs/k6/latest/javascript-api/k6-html/selection/selection-toarray/

val.name: val
val.documentation: Get the current value of the first element. https://grafana.com/docs/k6/latest/javascript-api/k6-html/selection/selection-val/

NodeType.name: NodeType
NodeType.signature: enum NodeType { ElementNode = 1, TextNode = 3, CommentNode = 8, DocumentNode = 9, DoctypeNode = 10, }

getElementsByTagName.name: getElementsByTagName
getElementsByTagName.documentation: Get descendant elements with tag name.

value.name: value
value.documentation: Value of `value` attribute if exists. Otherwise markup of content.

height.name: height
height.documentation: Coordinate space height in CSS pixels.

width.name: width
width.documentation: Coordinate space width in CSS pixels.

length.name: length
length.documentation: Number of contained form control elements.

host.name: host
host.documentation: URL hostname plus `:` delimited port if nonempty. `hostname[:port]`

port.name: port
port.documentation: URL port number. Empty string if unspecified.

length.name: length
length.documentation: Byte length of current text value.
